author: BigLibSB
title: His High School Friend Said...
text: Quote: Originally Posted by Twisted Sister Some people are jealous over a classmate's success and lash out with falsehoods and lies. Obama is not queer, born in Hawaii and was a community organizer in Chicago. Hell. I would be fascinated to have anybody verify whether or not she even attended the same school as him at the same time? Some people are attention seeking media whores. If this woman isn't a paid actress for a phone interview in the first place. Orly Taitz wants to get in touch with this woman.
